eu.cqse.check.util.clang

Class ClangTranslationUnitWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.cqse.check.util.clang.ClangTranslationUnitWrapper

  • public class ClangTranslationUnitWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrapper for the CXIndex type in Clang. This wrapper implements disposing the index (freeing the memory) when this Object is garbage collected.

    An "index" that consists of a set of translation units that would typically be linked together into an executable or library.

    • Method Detail

      • getMainTranslationUnit

        public eu.cqse.clang.SWIGTYPE_p_CXTranslationUnitImpl getMainTranslationUnit()
        Returns the current file parsed by clang. The clang index might contain more than one file (header files) which maybe lead to more than one translation unit known to clang. This is the translation unit corresponding to the file referenced in the current ICheckContext.
